-- U.S. Embassy in Brussels Evacuated on Suspicious Vehicle: Belga
-- B y   R e b e c c a   C h r i s t i e
-- 2012-09-05T13:01:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-05/u-s-embassy-in-brussels-evacuated-on-suspicious-vehicle-belga.html
The U.S. embassy in Brussels was
evacuated and surrounding streets were closed today due to a
suspicious vehicle parked nearby, Belga reported.  The embassy, consulate and the U.S. mission to the European
Union were evacuated as a precaution, the Belgian  news agency 
reported today. About 100 to 150 workers were affected, Belga
said, citing Belgian police and embassy press staff.  Spokespeople for the U.S. delegation did not immediately
respond to requests for comment from  Bloomberg News .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rebecca Christie in Brussels at 
 rchristie4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
